Shah discouraged d use of private planes by party officials for travel, other than during elections. He also followed the same. #WelcomeShah

The training campaign is moving at brisk pace towards achieving its ambitious target of 11 lakhs. #WelcomeShah
Party literature is being translated into regional languages & distributed across the organisation. #WelcomeShah
BJP performed well in Assembly Elections held during tenure of Shah.Out of 6 assembly elections held, BJP formed d govt in 4 #WelcomeShah
BJP took d bold step of contesting Haryana polls widout ny alliance & 1st BJP CM took oath in d state wid a majority on its own #WelcomeShah
BJP won a simple majority in Jharkhand & gv a stable govt to d state dat hs previously witnessed years of political instability #WelcomeShah
BJP got the highest vote share in J&K & became part of govt. with its Deputy CM for the first time since Independence. #WelcomeShah
